{"name":"Init.Control.Id","instances":[{"typeNames":["Id"],"name":"Id.instMonad","className":"Monad"},{"typeNames":["Id"],"name":"Id.instOfNat","className":"OfNat"},{"typeNames":["Id"],"name":"Id.instMonadLiftTOfPure","className":"MonadLiftT"}],"imports":["Init.Core"],"declarations":[{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/7c3ca70e29a0806bd4bfc62eae7084bbaf1a303d/src/Init/Control/Id.lean#L67-L68","name":"Id.instMonadLiftTOfPure","line":67,"kind":"instance","docLink":"./Init/Control/Id.html#Id.instMonadLiftTOfPure","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Control/Id.html#Id.instMonadLiftTOfPure\"><span class=\"name\">Id</span>.<span class=\"name\">instMonadLiftTOfPure</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">m</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> v</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Pure\">Pure</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#MonadLiftT\">MonadLiftT</a> <a href=\"./Init/Control/Id.html#Id\">Id</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/7c3ca70e29a0806bd4bfc62eae7084bbaf1a303d/src/Init/Control/Id.lean#L64-L65","name":"Id.instOfNat","line":64,"kind":"instance","docLink":"./Init/Control/Id.html#Id.instOfNat","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Control/Id.html#Id.instOfNat\"><span class=\"name\">Id</span>.<span class=\"name\">instOfNat</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#OfNat\">OfNat</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#OfNat\">OfNat</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Control/Id.html#Id\">Id</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/7c3ca70e29a0806bd4bfc62eae7084bbaf1a303d/src/Init/Control/Id.lean#L55-L62","name":"Id.run","line":55,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Control/Id.html#Id.run","doc":"Runs a computation in the identity monad.\n\nThis function is the identity function. Because its parameter has type `Id α`, it causes\n`do`-notation in its arguments to use the `Monad Id` instance.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Control/Id.html#Id.run\"><span class=\"name\">Id</span>.<span class=\"name\">run</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Control/Id.html#Id\">Id</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/7c3ca70e29a0806bd4bfc62eae7084bbaf1a303d/src/Init/Control/Id.lean#L49-L53","name":"Id.hasBind","line":49,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Control/Id.html#Id.hasBind","doc":"The identity monad has a `bind` operator.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Control/Id.html#Id.hasBind\"><span class=\"name\">Id</span>.<span class=\"name\">hasBind</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bind\">Bind</a> <a href=\"./Init/Control/Id.html#Id\">Id</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/7c3ca70e29a0806bd4bfc62eae7084bbaf1a303d/src/Init/Control/Id.lean#L43-L47","name":"Id.instMonad","line":43,"kind":"instance","docLink":"./Init/Control/Id.html#Id.instMonad","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Control/Id.html#Id.instMonad\"><span class=\"name\">Id</span>.<span class=\"name\">instMonad</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Monad\">Monad</a> <a href=\"./Init/Control/Id.html#Id\">Id</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/7c3ca70e29a0806bd4bfc62eae7084bbaf1a303d/src/Init/Control/Id.lean#L17-L39","name":"Id","line":17,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Control/Id.html#Id","doc":"The identity function on types, used primarily for its `Monad` instance.\n\nThe identity monad is useful together with monad transformers to construct monads for particular\npurposes. Additionally, it can be used with `do`-notation in order to use control structures such as\nlocal mutability, `for`-loops, and early returns in code that does not otherwise use monads.\n\nExamples:\n```lean example\ndef containsFive (xs : List Nat) : Bool := Id.run do\n  for x in xs do\n    if x == 5 then return true\n  return false\n```\n\n```lean example\n#eval containsFive [1, 3, 5, 7]\n```\n```output\ntrue\n```\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Control/Id.html#Id\"><span class=\"name\">Id</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">type</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u</div></div>"}]}